b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2793,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Regarding an Issue with the Team Change Mechanic","message":"<div>Quests on Master and Legend difficulty in Rise of the Sinister Dominion feature a mechanic that causes the boss to change their elemental attunement mid-battle. When this occurs, players must adapt to this new threat by changing their team, and therefore must prepare two teams before embarking on the quest.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>It has come to our attention that the following issues were occurring in these quests:<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>1. Players were able to begin the quest even if an adventurer on their first and second teams was equipped with the same (duplicate) portrait wyrmprint.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>2. If the player cleared the quest under the above conditions, an error could occur and the game would return to the title screen. However, we have confirmed that players were properly rewarded for clearing the quest regardless of whether or not such an error occurred.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>This issue has now been resolved.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1643004000,"prev_article_id":"2787","next_article_id":"10081","image_path":"","update_time":1643008575}}}'